# Talovka, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Talovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Talovsky Selsoviet, Tarumovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 7 streets.
Geography
Talovka is located 21&nbsp;km north of Tarumovka (the district's administrative centre) by road. Razdolye is the nearest rural locality.
